data.description: Come check out this amazing, one-of-a-kind, GABLE ROOF RANCH HOME. The home is open concept, comfortable, and cozy interior with the perfect layout. All bedrooms are all upstairs. The backyard has everything you can ask for, an upgraded patio, updated landscaping, a pond, a separate area where you can store an RV Diesel truck, or off-road equipment. The land is amazing. perfect place to add onto the property/ land or have amazing parties. The seller is ready to move!
